init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: While the four brothers were having dinner, the wolf knocked on the door.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The 92nd pig let him in and the wolf was shocked to see his three new friends.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The three pigs immediately became nervous and began to sweat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Can we help you?" asked the 92nd pig.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Oh no, i just came over to tell you guys that i have rebuilt my home and it is very nice!"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The three pigs looked at one another as if they were trying to figure out a way to say "isnt that nice" in the most sarcastic tone

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Well, we will let you be on your way."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf walked away and the three pigs hurried him to leave.
